& [SLMSlice29FixtureProviderEvidenceCoverage] is the source-complete slice for deterministic provider evidence fixture coverage
  + [slice_id] is SLM-29
  + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
  + [effort] is S
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-11, SLM-26, SLM-27, SLM-28
